cdc(change data capture) sql server

kafka platforms
- confluent(platform)
- pulsar

Use case(phase 1)
Transferring tables from 3 db to new back-office system, using CDC and Kafka connect API.

- CDC monitor all transaction log on repository source when change event happens it notifies kafka server.
- using Kafka Connect REST it take the change from source and deliver it to back-office db. 
 	
Steps:
1. connect to dev env.
2. check the pluralsight course. 
 


